{
  "page": "Blood of the Harpy",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Blood of the Harpy</b> is one of the titles assumed by <a href=\"/index.php/Hizdahr_zo_Loraq\" title=\"Hizdahr zo Loraq\">Hizdahr zo Loraq</a> after he assumes the <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Meereen\" title=\"King of Meereen\">throne</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> following the dissapperance of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Harpies\" title=\"Harpies\">harpy</a> is a symbol bore by the <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a> cities of <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> that references that of the <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Empire_of_Ghis\" title=\"Old Empire of Ghis\">Old Empire of Ghis</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blood_of_the_Harpy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Meereen\" title=\"King of Meereen\">King of Meereen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Scion_of_Ghis\" title=\"Scion of Ghis\">Scion of Ghis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Octarch_of_the_Old_Empire\" title=\"Octarch of the Old Empire\">Octarch of the Old Empire</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_the_Skahazadhan\" title=\"Master of the Skahazadhan\">Master of the Skahazadhan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Consort_to_Dragons\" title=\"Consort to Dragons\">Consort to Dragons</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=